parameters: 身穿粉色板甲的武者，看上去足够强大，一双明亮的眸子里透着 钢铁般的光芒，透着顽强的决心。不幸的是，她脸上的其余部分 是发痒的笑声。她的脖子是红色的，她的嘴是一条细细的、颤抖 的线，她的鼻孔张开。然而，事实上，这个场景看起来相当符合 圣经。她像被钉在十字架上一样伸展着四肢，被举到了空中。从 位置上看，您可能会认为两个天使雕像正在将她举起并支撑着 她，但您可以看到战士的手臂被天使的石质抓握在原地，他们的 另一只手挖入伸出的腋窝。

你可以听到刀刃在石头上微弱的叮当声，战士每只手都拿着一把 薄薄的刀刃，但这些半心半意的轻击几乎没有把石头切碎，因为 微笑、安详的天使继续用他们的石头手指在她的腋下涂鸦。仿佛 这对她腋窝的持续攻击还不够糟糕，天使的大翅膀向下伸到战士 的双脚上，那双脚裸露在外。石翅没有真正羽毛的绒毛，但由于 它们的设计很薄，它们是不错的挠痒工具，因为它们类似于几十 个微小的石刮。这些刮擦器在战士的脚上轻弹擦擦，你会听到更 多咕噜咕噜的笑声。
I wihihill never surrender, do yohohohohou hear me? Nehehehever!

天使们没有回答，只是继续挠痒痒。你的注意力也转移到了战士 苍白的脚上。你已经在发痒的胁迫下看到了足够多来观察各种反 应。许多人像触电一样连枷扭动，他们的脚移动得如此之快，几 乎是一片模糊。可以肯定，这是一种可爱的反应，但在美学上也 不是特别令人愉悦，因为它很难正确地欣赏和检查有问题的可爱 的脚。您很高兴地注意到，这位黑发斗士是喜欢坐着忍受折磨的 斗士之一。肯定有一些摆动和大量的咯咯笑声，但在大多数情况 下，除了偶尔的蜷缩和张开外，她纤细、精致、优雅的舞者脚仍 然在原位。这使您可以花时间欣赏她右脚跟上的胎记以及与她的 板甲同色系的粉红色脚趾甲。战士继续喊出更多无礼的挑战和挑 衅的嘲讽，但天使们继续以那种温和、仁慈的方式微笑，因为他 们的石头羽毛和手指将战士推向更深的愤怒的歇斯底里。
为她感到难过。让我们继续前进。
嘿，这会有用的! 让我们回到那个金发女记录者 身上。
灰尘，灰尘，灰尘... 哦，你好！我们又见面 了，人类！恐怕我正忙着打扫卫生，没空陪你 玩。Brock做了这个雕像，所以我必须尊重他努 力工作，并保持它漂亮和干净...

挠痒领主Matilda手里拿着一把鸡毛掸子，弯下身子眨了眨眼， 看起来就像是典型的轻浮法国女仆。她的行为也反映了这种戏弄 的行为。这座奇怪的栩栩如生的雕像被认为是一个年轻的战士， 一个有着相当突出的坚如磐石的勃起的年轻人。鸡毛掸子一次又 一次地扫过这个地方，缓慢而有节制地扫过石头的生殖器。你看 着雕像的表情，你会看到一张因发痒的痛苦而僵硬的脸——这座雕 塑一定是个天才，能够捕捉到如此栩栩如生的东西，一种欲望、 沮丧、快乐和痛苦的表情。
得让你一尘不染……呵呵呵呵，有事吗，人类？
那个雕像……是冒险者吗？那是一个真实的人吗？
估计以前也是，呵呵。Brock可以用他的力量把冒险者 变成石头。你最好避开他不好的一面。
嗯，是的，听起来确实很邪恶。
你看着Matilda为冒险家的蛋蛋打扫灰尘，而她俏皮的红指甲则 在他的轴头上爬行。你想知道冒险者怎么会被困在这种情况下， 他的字面意思是裤子掉下来，以便被冻结在这样的位置。
天哪，你怎么变得这么脏？人类，你为什么不跑呢？恐 怕还需要一段时间，我才能和他谈完。几个小时后变得 如此肮脏！在这之后得去弄他的腋窝，嘿嘿……
你看着Matilda为冒险家的蛋蛋打扫灰尘，而她俏皮的红指甲则 在他的轴头上爬行。你想知道冒险者怎么会被困在这种情况下， 他的字面意思是裤子掉下来，以便被冻结在这样的位置。
你会看到一个看起来像是童话故事的景象——一个金色的骑士与一 条巨大的龙战斗！可眼下，石龙却在光荣的胜利中游荡。棕发战 士身穿闪闪发光的金色盔甲，被钉住并被困住，她的巨剑从她手 中被击落。这条龙把它的大尾巴盘在她的下半身，用它的长爪子 抓着她穿袜子的脚。剪断的靴子被丢弃在附近。

你看着身穿盔甲的女人用戴着手套的拳头猛击巨龙的侧翼。敲击 的声音很大，但巨龙耸了耸肩，继续用爪子在女人穿袜子的脚上 上下划动。薄薄的白色棉布对石龙又长又钝的爪子几乎没有提供 足够的防御，你会看到每一次向上的击球都会让脚趾像防御者举 起盾牌一样嘎吱作响，而向下的每一击都会让脚趾像防御者一样 张开探出头来看看是否安全，只是在下一次中风到来时才匆匆回 到安全的地方。巨龙保持着这一点，每只脚各用一只爪子，上下 挑逗，而金色的战士呻吟着，用高跷的细高跟笑声拉紧。看得出 来，她的笑都是不情愿的，她不断地用拳头敲打着龙的腿和尾 巴，虽然她还不如试图打破一座山。
女人抬头看着你们两个，她棕色的眼睛充满希望地睁大。
Rally toho me! Hehehelp me escape, gah, please! Heh, urgh...
可惜，你细细的手臂和纤细的身躯，在挠痒痒的时候并没有什么 缺点，但在这个游戏世界里，你连举剑都太弱了。甚至需要你和 Cissy一起搬运它，但即便如此，你也必须将它拖到地上，而且 你甚至无法准确和有力地挥动它。
呃，你怎么在战斗中使用这个东西？
你向战士道歉地耸了耸肩，但她现在正忙着笑而没有注意到。这 条龙已经开始在她薄薄的白色袜子上使用它的舌头和尾巴（这些 袜子现在看起来又破又破，所以她的脚可能很快就会光着脚，并 且处于更加可怕的状态）。
Look at the golden fighter again?

Oooh, I wonder what we have here?
你惊讶地转过身来，胸部突然打开并吞没了你！看来你的贪婪已 经把你带进了挠痒痒的陷阱！胸部似乎是某种模仿物，它吞没了 你的半个身体，只有你的手臂和躯干是自由的。你可以感觉到模 仿者在“咀嚼”你，舌头在咕噜咕噜地滑动，多节的木头牙齿在你 身上戳戳和翻找。
Ahahahaha, gehehehet me out of hehehehere!
我在努力! 这东西动不了！
啊，你在求救吗？我看到你有点受束缚，有点痒痒的小 人。想出去吗？
嗯，我愿意用一个有趣的双关语来交换! 这太公平了！
我来帮你，兄弟！昨天，一个小丑为我开门。真是个不 错的小丑！
多好的小丑啊！哈哈哈哈！
很难理解她为什么要把我们从她制造的陷阱中解放出 来，我得说......

You see an adventure who has let her avarice get the better of her — she’s thrown open a chest in search of loot, only to find a tentacle tickle trap in the chest! The ash-haired woman must have some superhuman reflexes, as she was very close to avoiding the trap — she must have turned and leapt as soon as she opened it and saw there was a nasty surprise waiting for her. The tentacles in the chest are at full extension, but they’ve only been able to snare her ankles and nothing more. It seems to be a stalemate, as the tentacles tug and the ashen-haired girl grunts and holds onto the ground, her fingers grabbing onto a tree for leverage.
What’s that adventurer thinking, opening every chest she sees? What a silly goose.
You say that as if we haven’t done that dozens of times.
Looks like you could use a hand, huh?

You hear a rip as the tentacles tear off the leather soles of the female adventurer’s boots. Seconds later, her arms shake and angry titters fly from her pursed lips as the tentacles introduce themselves to her bare soles. From the way her fingers are trembling for purchase, the tickling must be quite intense (or her feet very sensitive — or perhaps both).
Urgh, yes! Huhuhuhurry! Grahahaha! Why dididihid it have to be tickling! My trahahahining never prepared me for thihihihihis! What kind of monster ch-ch-ch-chest is thihihihis?
Ah, you like my chest, do you? Works wonders on nosy adventurers such as yourself.

In a valiant attempt, the ashen-haired girl goes for the sword on her back, but Matilda ducks, and after the sword goes whizzing over her head. Giggling, Matilda slips her fingers in the armpit while she has a chance, and the adventurer shrieks with laughter. The chest swallows the girl up to her thighs, and from the sound of her anguished laughter, the things it's doing to her toes, feet, knees, and thighs can’t be anything good. If that weren’t bad enough, Matilda sits on the girl’s back and digs her nails into both armpits at once.
Oooh, she’s really rumbling under me! Guess she’s one of those super defiant ticklish types, huh?
The adventurer tries to reach back to jab backwards with her sword, but Matilda reaches out and snaps the blade in half as easily if it were a twig.
None of that now, just focus on breathing and laughing, hehehehe... but I tell you what, I’ll stop tickling you if you can tell me a joke.
I’m no jehehester to ehehentertain you!

Is that so? Hmmm, are your toes ticklish, I wonder? I spied a bit of black nail varnish on them, so I take it you pamper them a fair bit? Let’s send a few tentacles to explore under and between them and see what we find...
Oh, the toes are ticklish? Ah, as I hoped! Let’s keep this up till we get a good joke from you, yes? Or maybe you want to keep going? Who am I to understand human inclinations...

The chest gulps another few inches of the ticklish adventurer, claiming her waist as well. From the way her green eyes flicker and the angry moan of laughter, the tentacles have taken to exploring this new spot with cruel curiosity. You imagine they’re doing all sorts of deviously diabolical things to her womanhood to make her gasp and groan like that.
Matilda turns you to with an amused shrug.
She says stop, but she doesn’t say a joke to make me stop. Guess she needs some time to think of one. I’ll come back later.
With a final parting poke in the ribs, the Tickle Lord flies away, leaving the ashen-haired adventurer to curse and splutter with more despondent laughter.
Um, need some help thinking of a joke?
I'm not plahahaying along for thahahat wretch!
Up to you, I guess. Enjoy the tickles.

The sight of the silvery blue marble serpent tickling the Chronicler fills you with questions. Where did this creature come from? Was it sculpted by the Tickle Lord’s magic? Was the marble already here, or was it brought here for some nefarious purpose? You suppose the moored ship beside the shore may provide some answers, but you’ve already kinda lost interest. The peril of the squealing blonde Chronicler is far more immediate and relevant.
You thehehere! Can you plehehehease hehehelp!?

You consider asking her questions about the origins of the marble, but you decide to hold off for now. The pretty Chronicler is on the ground, with her ankles locked in the jaws of the marble serpent statue. The two other serpents seem to be licking her feet with tongues of pale marble, and although they leave now saliva behind, you can see the woman gasping and groaning with very flick. The Chronicler seems to read your expression and answers your unasked question, flushing.
Thehehe marble is reheheally cold! It feels sohoho tingly, ahahaha!

You watch the precious metal glint in the dim light. As thin and flexible as any true snake, the tongues dance upon every curve and crevice of the Chronicler’s long milky soles. You watch for a while, quirking a knowing eyebrow as the Chronicler’s feet splay while she moans with laughter. Those tongues really are something. You watch as those pale tongues flick and caress the centres of the pale soles before moving up to lap and swipe at the long, unpainted toes. It’s no wonder the Chronicler is a heaving, chortling mess with three of those tongues slinking and stroking across her soles.
Erm, those snake things look pretty tough, and I’d rather not fight them. Think you can answer our questions while they’re tickling you?
Whahahahat? You’re suhuhupposed to be heheroes! Hehehelp me first! Help my pooohohoor feet!
Uh, we’re not adventurers and we’re not heroes. We’re also kinda weak.
I dohoho not wish to hear your ehehexcuses! Hehelp me get a breheheak or I’m not telling you ahahanything!
You know if you give us the information, it’ll help us beat the Tickle Lords and theoretically free you more quickly, right? Where’s your sense of duty as a Chronicler?
The blonde Chronicler bursts out a roar of laughter as two of the marble serpent’s tongues start snaking through her toes.
Nohohoho, nohohot my tohohohoes! Grrrahaha, I’m sehehehelfish, ohohokay? You don’t hehelp me, I don’t hehelp you, and that’s fihihinal, hahahahaha!
My, how stubborn. Guess we better find a way then. Ideas, sister?
Well, the easiest thing would be to find a bomb or something to blow up those statues.
Yeah, that would be easy. But let’s say we didn’t have anything like that and just had to make do with the garbage lying around.
Hmm, maybe we could find a rag or something to wrap around her feet? Then she’d at least get a breather while they figured out how to rip them off.
I don’t know, sis. I mean, they figured out how to take her shoes and socks off easily enough.
Thahahat was my ohohohown fahahahault! I took my sh-sh-shoes off and was rehehehesting with my feeheet in the water, gahahahaha!
Well, that wasn’t very smart when dealing with a land ruled by Tickle Lords, was it? Anyway, sit tight. We'll do what we can. Just keep your word!
Hmm, maybe we could find a rag or something to wrap around her feet? Then she’d at least get a breather while they figured out how to rip them off.
Hmm, maybe we could find a rag or something to wrap around her feet? Then she’d at least get a breather while they figured out how to rip them off.

You drape the heavy black cloak over the Chronicler's bare feet, winding and knotting it several times. Two of the serpents keep on 'licking' away, but the third seems perplexed, poking and trying to dislodge the dark cloth. You have some time to talk now, but you're not sure how much.
The Chronicler gulps in air, still twitching a little as the serpent statues paw at her feet.
Alright, ask your questions. And thank you...
Grey-skinned, dark haired, and notoriously without mercy. He possess some kind of sorcery that animates statues, turns them into his slaves. He's a menace, and I'd avoid him at all costs.

Hard to comprehend her. I've seen her traps ensnare a few of the knights I was assigned too, but after tormenting them a while, she'd let them go. I don't understand what she's trying to do. Maybe she's toying with us? Or maybe she secretly wants us to overthrow her and Brock? I don't know.
Free the adventurers? If we could mass up and fight the Tickle Lords, we might have a chance...
How'd that go for you last time?
Very poorly. We got lost in the ruins, stumbled into traps, or picked off.
Or in your case, voluntarily took off her shoes and got tickled silly for it.
No need to bring that up! Anyway, if you can't free the others, perhaps you could try to drive a wedge between the Tickle Lords? I don't know, but they seem to have a complicated relationship.
Hmmmm, that's not a terrible idea...

No clue, I'm afraid. Matilda can fly and whizz around, but at least Brock tends to be easier to anticipate with those big heavy footsteps of his. But he already seems to know what's going on. I think his statues are his informants...
Alright, that’s enough from you two. Matilda may insist on ignoring the very real threat that you are, but I’m not tolerating it any longer.
Oh, Brock, hey! I was about to deal with those two!
Is that so? My statues hear everything in these ruins, and what they heard is a dereliction of duty.
Brock, you know it turns me on when you use fancy words, but could you speak plainly please?
Get out of my way. You’re not dealing with them, so I am. Now.
Think we'd best beat a hasty retreat, bro.

The end of the Chronicler's sentence is punctuated by a ripping sound and a squeal, as the serpents tear apart the rag that had shrouded and protected her sensitive bare feet. The tongues flick and stroke over them deftly and swiftly, even faster than before as if making up for lost time, and the pretty blonde young woman is quickly tickled back into hysterics as the tongue carve across all the familiarly devastating hot spots across her feet.
Don't think there's much we can do for you now. Sorry!
Welcome all! Please make yourself at home <3
A Chronicler! Got a pretty obvious question for you that we hope you can answer -- what exactly is going on with the two Tickle Lords here?
Hehehehe, hehehelp me down fihihihirst! Plehehease, hahahandsome!

Unfortunately, there isn't really a ton that you can do. The Chronicler is bound tightly to the stone slab ornament, with rocky hands emerging from the sides of it to prod her sides and grab her ribs. Further hands lift up her ankles so another set of hands can scrabble across her pale soles, which you can help but notice are unusually pretty for a Chronicler, with a silver anklet, pink nail varnish, and even a toe-ring on one foot. It's really quite strange considering your impression of the profession of Chroniclers is basically a notch above working-class.
I don't think we can help you, sorry. We don't have any sledgehammers on us. Say, why have you got such fancy feet? Not what I expected from a Chronicler, not that I'm complaining.
She was probably trying to bag herself a husband or paramour among the adventurers here. Look at those curls... I know the type.
Guhuhuhuh, I am nohohohot gohohonna talk about mehehehee!
Yeah, that's a yes. But let's move on.
Nohoho! I'm nohohot gonna talk to you if you're gohohohonna be mehehean to me, hahaha!
You reach out and goose her ribs. Cissy chuckles and goes along, raking her long nails over the Chronicler's insteps.
Wahahahahaha! Alright, stop, stop, stahahahap! It's alreheheheady bahahad enohohough!

You and Cissy stop tickling, though the stone hands continue digging and scrabbling across her spots. The pretty Chronicler pants and gulps down air as best as she can from this reduced tickling, though it's still pretty intense.
Alright, give us some info so we can help you, okay? We wanna know how to defeat the Tickle Lords here. Have you encountered them?
Tickle Lord! Kihihinda handsome in a ruhuhugged kinda way! Grey skin! Controls the statues! He dihihihid this toohoho mehehe!
The Chronicler gestures downwards to her tickle-ravaged body, but it's hardly necessary. You get the picture.
Rehehed hair! A pihihihixie, I thihink! She mahahade many trahahaps around here!
We know to be careful, thanks.
I think she reheheheally fancied hihihim! But he just wahahasn't that intohohoho heheheher!
We kinda got that impression too. Ah, the pangs of unrequited love. Wonder how we can use that to our advantage.
I think the bihihig guy is somewhere to the north, ahahaha! No idea for the gihihihirl!
Alright, that’s enough from you two. Matilda may insist on ignoring the very real threat that you are, but I’m not tolerating it any longer.
Oh, Brock, hey! I was about to deal with those two!
Is that so? My statues hear everything in these ruins, and what they heard is a dereliction of duty.
Brock, you know it turns me on when you use fancy words, but could you speak plainly please?
Get out of my way. You’re not dealing with them, so I am. Now.
Think we'd best beat a hasty retreat, bro.
Thanks, pretty thing. We'll do what we can to get you out.
Thanks, pretty thing. We'll do what we can to get you out.

Inside the chest, you find a stuffed animal. From how worn and faded the colours are, you surmise it’s quite old indeed. You don’t really want to log around a big teddy bear, so you just stuff it back inside.
Oooh, a chest! But there's nothing in here, not even a trap... lame.

You reach you hand in and slowly pull out a small worn book from the chest. You flip open the book and see it’s a diary written in a youthful scrawl. It’s probably Tickle Lord Matilda’s? You look at the latest entry.

Brock gave me flowers yesterday. Well, not truly flowers — they were herbs he found from the ground. He said I should eat them for a healthier diet and not just relying on mirth and lust energy. Isn’t he sweet?
